name: Blessed prayer
description: When I come to a place, such as Mount Binaiya on a Seram island, my shame. there is a suggestion for a permit and informing the local community that they will be climbing. before the trip, usually we will perform a ceremony and read a prayer, so that along the way we are always given ease and smoothness until we come back down to the village. This moment was taken while climbing Mount Biniaya on December 28 2016.
